<template>

</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "OpenShare",
  data() {
    return {
      code: this.$root.quert.code,
      shareId: this.$root.quert.shareId,
      share: {},
      validate: false
    }
  },

  created() {
    this.load()
  },
  methods: {
    load() {
      this.$request.get('/share/selectById/' + this.shareId).then((res) => {
        this.share = res.data || {}

        //验证code对不对
        this.share.code !== this.code
      })
    },
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
